# Language in codebase

- **Code, comments, javadocs, commit messages, and in-repo documentation** (e.g. AGENTS.md, README in code packages) must be written in **English**.
- **User-facing strings** (i18n message keys and values in `.properties`, UI copy, bot messages) may be in any language; they are not part of the "code" rule.
- Exception messages and log messages that appear in code should be in English so that logs and stack traces are readable by any developer.

Apply this rule consistently so the agent does not revert to another language for comments or docs.
